    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "The Tiger",
        "Description": "A Tiger is one of the most distinct animals one may see out there.\r\rThe crepuscular cat is brazen with orange and black stripes, with white ocelli merely complementing their fur coats. Their jaws can open up and pierce the flesh of their prey.\r\rFlashes of orange and white are all the prey can see, whether they roam or they sit in one places, one could not avoid the stripes and the fangs of the Tiger until the herd is culled by one territorial carnivore.\r\rSurely a tale to tell.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Ashley.\r\rFC72",
